organization.title: NHS Erewash CCG
organization.description:
NHS Erewash CCG has representation from 
all the GP practices in our area. We have 
a Governing Body made up of local GPs,
supported by lay members and NHS staff.
We are made up of 12 GP practices from
Ilkeston, Sandiacre and Long Eaton. The GPs
work with the CCG and the local Councils to
plan local health and wellbeing services for the
local people
